{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1717223103.319377", "card_id": "Q_657778531", "card_label": {"type": "boiling", "icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8ec286ae756c2ab8377774b27f8ebc7_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-022e7c409e51515f784aa70403aef8d4_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1252}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "胡塞武装称为了回应美英空袭，已袭击美国「艾森豪威尔」号航母，双方局势会进一步升级吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "△当地时间 30 日，美英对也门首都萨那、荷台达多地发动空袭 当地时间 5 月 31 日，也门胡塞武装军事发言人叶海亚·萨雷亚表示，美英对也门首都萨那、荷台达多地空袭，共导致至少 16 人死亡、 42 人受伤。 叶海亚·萨雷亚表示，美英空袭针对当地民用设施违反国际法，犯有战争罪。作为对美英袭击的回应，胡塞武装已针对美军的「艾森豪威尔」号航空母舰进行袭击。（总台记者 朱云翔） 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4fe8ff810796b43767f366cbc41c5e3e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2925 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657778531"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr/KdoZ2R59IQEAMaCTEwODQ1MDgwOCDm5uayBjAAOM0UQAByCTY1Nzc3ODUzMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1717223103.320916", "card_id": "Q_657778941", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 179}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价孙楠在《歌手 2024》第四期演唱的《拯救》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-939b5635ba5189aeae4999aca39336e0_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "359 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657778941"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr/KdoZ2R59IQEAMaCTEwODQ1MDg5NSDR7OayBjAAOL4CQAFyCTY1Nzc3ODk0MXgAqg